    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "Thanks @andymac4182. That's very cool indeed to be able to send URLs generated by the routing. However I think that with your change, we're loosing some information. The formatted parameters contains all the parameters exhaustively and the nbHits provides informations about the number of results computed by Algolia.\r\n\r\nCan you maybe add your change as an alternative piece of information that people might want to use?",
