  {
    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "@bobylito Personally in the case of Google Analytics it doesn't make sense to send a URL that never existed and might not actually work. If there is extra parameters that aren't shown in the URL that aren't a default I would be surprised. \r\n\r\nI think doing a manual format of the URL should be for advanced users personally since I would imagine most people would be similar to myself and just want the correct page view stats which is based on the routing. ",
